languages.text: "Это псайкер — я чувствую, как варп-силы клубятся вокруг нее. Одна из пленниц культистов. Как ей удалось выбраться из клетки и уцелеть? Будь начеку: подобные ей представляют собой опасность даже когда не желают никому навредить".

"She is a psyker — I can feel warp emanations roiling around her. One of the cultists' prisoners. How did she manage to get out of the cage and survive? Be vigilant — creatures like her remain dangerous even when they mean to do no harm."

languages.text: “她是个灵能者，我感觉到她周围散发着亚空间的气息。她之前被那些邪教徒关起来了，但她究竟是怎么逃出牢笼，存活下来的？要保持警惕，像他这样的怪物哪怕没有主观恶意，也非常危险。”

languages.text: «Es psíquica. Puedo sentir las emanaciones de disformidad que se arremolinan en torno a ella. Es una prisionera de los sectarios. ¿Cómo ha logrado escapar de su jaula y sobrevivir? Tenga cuidado, esta clase de criaturas es peligrosa incluso cuando no quiere hacer daño a nadie».
languages.original_text: "She is a psyker — I can feel warp emanations roiling around her. One of the cultists' prisoners. How did she manage to get out of the cage and survive? Be vigilant — creatures like her remain dangerous even when they mean to do no harm."

languages.text: 「アレは異能者か…あの女の周りでゆらゆらと歪みが溢れ出るのを感じます。教団の囚人のひとりですね。どうやって檻を出て死なずにいたんだ？気をつけてください…ああいったモノは、危害を加えるつもりがなくても十分危険です」

languages.text: "Sie ist eine Psionikerin – ich spüre eine Warp-Ausstrahlung um sie herum. Eine Gefangene der Kultisten. Wie konnte sie aus dem Käfig entkommen und überleben? Seid wachsam – Kreaturen wie sie bleiben gefährlich, auch wenn sie nichts Böses wollen."
languages.original_text: "She is a psyker — I can feel warp emanations roiling around her. One of the cultists' prisoners. How did she manage to get out of the cage and survive? Be vigilant — creatures like her remain dangerous even when they mean to do no harm."

languages.text: « C'est une psyker, je sens les émanations du Warp tout autour d'elle. L'une des prisonnières des cultistes. Je me demande comment elle est parvenue à s'échapper et à survivre. Restez sur vos gardes. Même quand elles n'ont aucune intention de faire le mal, ces créatures demeurent particulièrement dangereuses. »

languages.text: "Bir Ruhsezer... Öteboyut uçumları etrafında dalgalanıyor, sezebiliyorum. Tarikatçıların mahkûmlarından. Kafesten kaçıp hayatta kalmayı nasıl başarmış? Tedbiri elden bırakmayalım. Türü, art niyetli olmasa bile tehlikelidir."
languages.original_text: "She is a psyker — I can feel warp emanations roiling around her. One of the cultists' prisoners. How did she manage to get out of the cage and survive? Be vigilant — creatures like her remain dangerous even when they mean to do no harm."

traits.locale_text: "Bir Ruhsezer… Öteboyut uçumlarının etrafında dalgalandığını sezebiliyorum. Tarikatçıların mahkûmlarından biri olduğu aşikâr. Kafesten kaçıp hayatta kalmayı nasıl başardı? Tedbiri elden bırakmayın. Onun türü, art niyetli olmasa bile tehlikelidir."
